{"tid":779874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第時香港獨立邊個做總統？","createTime":"2018-08-14T17:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T11:25:15.000Z","uid":153689,"like":38,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8e134341ea79e80a1676c8b9d8752af1281d3f3d","tid":779874,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"梁振英定陳浩天？<br />\n<br />\n梁振英唔洗講，多得佢一直吹奏港獨先帶起大家討論。由民族論到今日FCC，如果冇左佢都冇咁多人討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民族論俾佢吹奏到賣斷晒貨，FCC單野俾佢搞到全香港人都知，連外媒都特登出文回應佢。好多嘢身後都有佢嘅影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港獨之父嘅名當之無愧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我懷疑佢已經有晒plan要點做<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天，唔晒講由組黨到依家做左好多事。迫到政府撕爛塊面，搞到港獨依個topic上到外媒報導，又有同其他組織連繫。<br />\n咁多次發言嘅表現亦都有目共睹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將來明面上嘅港獨代表人物應該都係佢<br />\n<br />\n真係好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4df11a93cecb152fce3746c15c3e38523e16338","tid":779874,"uid":13504,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:15:04.000Z","msg":"港豬: 劉華, 發哥"},{"pid":"8d5608f12cfeaf25a52f00932b8c72e9b5a4b17f","tid":779874,"uid":6347,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:16:32.000Z","msg":"請侵侵黎做<br />\nMake hong kong great again"},{"pid":"866a75fc34ed43de42df510ee6dd7ee114fb8b5f","tid":779874,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T17:17:44.000Z","msg":"陳浩天大總統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梁天琦總理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關元帥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已